ment of the\nfirst numerical method for fully resolved simulation of fusion filament\nmodeling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Nov 2017 22:27:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Feb 2018 22:43:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-27"}
